headline: Amcor recognized with prestigious award for recycle-ready coffee packaging
summary: Amcor (NYSE: AMCR, ASX:AMC), a global leader in developing and producing responsible packaging solutions has been recognized by the 35th Packaging Innovation Awards (PIA) for its AmPrima® Plus solution for coffee.
